Class DataAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataAnalysis

  • public abstract class DataAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
    This class calculates several metrics based off of the reservations and cancellations csv files This class is abstract and all the methods are static since instances are not needed to calculate the various metrics

      • getRoomsOfHotelInString

        private static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> getRoomsOfHotelInString(java.util.ArrayList<TypeOfRoom> rooms)
        Helper function that places all TypeOfRoom objects in "rooms" into a HashMap with TypeOfRoom-Integer pairs. This will be used in the occupancy and income calculations to keep track of every room's occupancy/income.
        Parameters:
        rooms - A list of TypeOfRoom objects.
        Returns:
        A HashMap mapping the names of each room in "rooms" to Integers
